code: @Bean @ConditionalOnMissingBean public DynatraceMeterRegistry dynatraceMeterRegistry(DynatraceConfig dynatraceConfig, Clock clock) {     return DynatraceMeterRegistry.builder(dynatraceConfig).clock(clock).httpClient(new HttpUrlConnectionSender(this.properties.getConnectTimeout(), this.properties.getReadTimeout())).build(). }
